": 316, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4313138727028743e-21, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an injury scare\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"a leg problem\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive frame\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite more than her share of setbacks, including an agonising early exit at the Tokyo Olympics because of injury, the 31-year-old who claimed her second world gold last year tells Metro she would change nothing about her journey.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her share\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"setbacks\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"an agonising early exit\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"her second world gold\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"her journey\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manchester was good in parts, those two events have been going really well in training and I wanted to see them put together in a competition environment.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999995093276, \"rank\": 2.4165635008232184e-10, \"text\": \"Manchester\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parts\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"those two events\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition environment\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not get the result I wanted in the javelin [finishing ninth with 42.38metres] but I did in the 200m [runner-up toDina Asher-Smithin 23.20 seconds].\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"the javelin\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"42.38metres\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"runner-up toDina\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"23.20 seconds\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a cold, wet, windy day and I wasn't expecting that much.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cold, wet, windy day\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had two goals: I had not run a 200m this year so wanted to get the mark there so that I can be in the final heat in France.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998221119659504, \"rank\": 0.00017488080040944855, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two goals\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"a 200m\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the mark\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"the final heat\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really, really shocked at doing that time in those conditions.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"those conditions\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a good weekend overall.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston has been pivotal.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aston\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been able to turn those hard times around, I feel he gives me strength.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those hard times\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy with the mindset he has helped me work on.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mindset\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He reinforces me with facts and is so calm, and so I believe everything he says.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"facts\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not give credit easily, so it means something when he does.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"credit\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston has [helped athletes win] so many medals in the sport and his experience is invaluable in that sense.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aston\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"so many medals\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"his experience\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"that sense\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I never really show fitness or form going into a heptathlon so that's normal for me!\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"a heptathlon\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I put it together every time and it's fine.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I can get to the startline fit and healthy I always believe I have a real chance.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the startline fit\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"a real chance\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel I have got unfinished business at the Olympics, I just feel those Olympic experiences have not gone as I wanted them to.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unfinished business\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"those Olympic experiences\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to give myself a really good chance in Paris.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really good chance\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be able to say wherever I finish in the field that I will have given my best performance.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"my best performance\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally I let myself down in Rio and it was the opposite in Tokyo where I was in a really good place mentally but not physically.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999719102566, \"rank\": 2.808977313835379e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6981527295284217, \"rank\": 0.4323511150007434, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good place\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing has gone perfectly.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I have gained good experience from every single one I have been to, for example the crowd from 2012 - and I think we will get something similar in Paris - or the pressure that was on me in Rio in 2016.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999719102566, \"rank\": 2.808977313835379e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good experience\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"every single one\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I am in a strong place and my body is in a healthy place now.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong place\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"a healthy place\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it's about taking it day by day ahead of Paris.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One hundred per cent.\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a lot of downs in my story as well as the ups but when I look back, I feel lucky.\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"the ups\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have overcome the harder times and then come through that to the other side and won the world title again in Budapest last year.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.999486657478019, \"rank\": 0.0005136061778537639, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the harder times\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"the world title\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not change a thing about my story.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British Gas commissioned a mural for me in my home city and it is absolutely incredible.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3004, \"end\": 3015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"score\": 0.9830961297432252, \"rank\": 0.009499152226353233, \"text\": \"British Gas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mural\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"my home city\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the second time I have worked with the artist Paul Curtis, who is a local legend.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3144, \"end\": 3155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.8775081799577619, \"rank\": 0.13131313131310177, \"text\": \"Paul Curtis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second time\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"the artist\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"a local legend\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It says on it 'You will never run alone' as a nod to the team I support, Liverpool.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.247588119029565e-13, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a luckier career than most have.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a luckier career\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it does not happen, I have been very fortunate and I do not want people feeling sorry for me.\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will go there and give it my all to get the result I want.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British Gas has commissioned a 30-metre mural ofKatarina Johnson-Thompsonfeaturing motivational phrases proven to power positivity, with the aim of supporting the heptathlete and inspiring the local Liverpool community ArrowMORE:Jessica Ennis-Hill backs Katarina Johnson-T